x.diagram:
digraph {

graph [layout = "dot",
       outputorder = "edgesfirst",
       bgcolor = "white"]

node [fontname = "Helvetica",
      fontsize = "10",
      shape = "circle",
      fixedsize = "true",
      width = "0.5",
      style = "filled",
      fillcolor = "aliceblue",
      color = "gray70",
      fontcolor = "gray50"]

edge [fontname = "Helvetica",
     fontsize = "8",
     len = "1.5",
     color = "gray80",
     arrowsize = "0.5"]

  "1" [label = "A"] 
  "2" [label = "B"] 
  "3" [label = "C"] 
  "4" [label = "D"] 
  "5" [label = "E"] 
  "1"->"2" 
  "2"->"4" 
  "3"->"4" 
  "4"->"5" 
}
